::Astroblast/Drag Strip/Switchblade::

Astroblast's radar picks up the base signal as he approaches, 
"Motormaster, we have almost arrived, prepare for landing. Also, I 
picked up a curious Maximal energy signal on my radar while we 
were over the Atlantic. It appeared to be traveling towards south-
eastern North America. We may wan't to investigate."

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Drag Strip follows Speedbreaker and Wildrider into the ship, the 
Dark Avian.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Switchblade hops up as the commlink crackles to life with 
Motormaster's voice. "Well what do ya know, or at least what do I 
know, this is Motormaster, and you're talking to Switchblade, or 
Switchblade is talking to you, which ever you prefer, and I am 
pleased to meet you, and I think that Skullgrin and Cyclonus and 
Scourge, and... no wait, there's nobody else here who's new. Oh, 
by the way, this is the Dark Avian, we read you loud and clear." He 
says cheerfully not aware of all the useless information he has told 
to Motormaster.
